  <title>Avogadro constant</title>
  <index>constant</index>
  <termversion>3.0.1</termversion>
  <lastupdated>2020-03-30</lastupdated>
  <definitions>
    <item>
      <id>1</id>
      <text>Fundamental physical constant (symbols: L,) representing the molar number of entities: .</text>
      <notes>
        <item>In the revision of the International System of Units (SI) of 2019 the Avogadro constant became one of the seven defining constants with the exact value 6.022 140 76 x 10E23 mol-1.</item>
        <item>The Avogadro number is the exact numerical value of the Avogadro constant, 6.022 140 76 x 10E23</item>
        <item>While the symbol NA is used to honour Amedeo Avogadro, the symbol L is used in honour of Josef Loschmidt.</item>
      </notes>
      <links>
        <item>
          <title>entities</title>
          <url>https://goldbook.iupac.org/terms/view/N04266</url>
        </item>
        <item>
          <title>amount of substance</title>
          <url>https://goldbook.iupac.org/terms/view/A00297</url>
        </item>
      </links>
      <math>
        <item>
          <meaning>Avogadro constant (2019)</meaning>
          <type>constant</type>
          <alttext>NA = 6.022 140 76 x 10E23 mol-1</alttext>
          <latex>N_{\rm{A}} = \pu{6.02214076E23 mol-1}</latex>
        </item>
        <item>
          <meaning>amount of substance</meaning>
          <type>symbol</type>
          <alttext>n</alttext>
          <latex>n</latex>
        </item>
        <item>
          <meaning>number of entities</meaning>
          <type>symbol</type>
          <alttext>N</alttext>
          <latex>N</latex>
        </item>
        <item>
          <meaning>equation relating number of entities to the Avogadro constant multiplied by the amount of substance</meaning>
          <type>equation</type>
          <alttext>N=N_A.n</alttext>
          <latex>N = N_{\text{A}}\ n</latex>
        </item>
        <item>
          <meaning>Avogadro constant value with unit (2019)</meaning>
          <type>numeric value with unit</type>
          <alttext>6.022 140 76 x 10E23 mol-1</alttext>
          <latex>\pu{6.02214076E23 mol-1}</latex>
        </item>
        <item>
          <meaning>Avogadro constant value (2019)</meaning>
          <type>numeric value with unit</type>
          <alttext>6.022 140 76 x 10E23</alttext>
          <latex>6.022\ 140\ 76 \times 10^{23}</latex>
        </item>
        <item>
          <meaning>Avogadro constant (2019)</meaning>
          <type>symbol</type>
          <alttext>NA</alttext>
          <latex>N_{\text{A}}</latex>
        </item>
        <item>
          <meaning>Avogadro symbol (Josef Loschmidt)</meaning>
          <type>symbol</type>
          <alttext>L</alttext>
          <latex>L</latex>
        </item>
      </math>
