        <item>BIPM, Le Système international d’unités (SI), SI Brochure, 9e ed. (2019), p. 17 (https://www.bipm.org/fr/publications/si-brochure/)</item>
        <item>BIPM, The International System of Units, SI Brochure, 9th ed. (2019), p. 129 (https://www.bipm.org/en/publications/si-brochure/)</item>
        <item>Green Book, 3rd ed. (https://doi.org/10.1039/9781847557889)</item>
      </sources>
    </item>
